Class InventoryCsvWriter

java.lang.Object
com.amilesend.discogs.csv.InventoryCsvWriter
All Implemented Interfaces:
AutoCloseable
public class InventoryCsvWriter extends Object implements AutoCloseable
Utility to write an inventory CSV file used for Discogs inventory management (i.e., creating new inventory items, or update existing inventory items).
